\id 2TH - Dobu NT [dob] -Papua New Guinea 1985 (web version -2013)
\h 2 TESALONAIKA
\toc1 Me Tesalonaika ꞌIdi Leta ꞌEluwena Paulo ꞌIꞌetoladina
\toc2 2 Tesalonaika
\toc3 2 Te
\mt1 ME TESALONAIKA ꞌIDI LETA
\mt1 ꞌELUWENA PAULO ꞌIꞌETOLADINA
\ip Muliyega Paulo me Tesalonaika tetelidi ꞌinonona ꞌaene nigeya sinuwanuwa sabwalena Yesu ꞌina ilalimana baleꞌuya manuna. Gete manuna ꞌidi leta ꞌeluwena ꞌiꞌetoladina.
\c 1
\s1 Lokagutoki
\p 
\v 1 ꞌAboꞌama Sailasa be Timoti maꞌegwao ꞌimi leta ꞌaꞌetoꞌetoladinawa ꞌomi toekalesiyao Tesalonaika ꞌenaya, manuna ꞌomi Tamada Yaubada be ꞌInapwana Yesu Keliso ꞌadi toemisao.
\v 2 Tamada Yaubada be ꞌida ꞌInapwana Yesu Keliso ꞌidi obobomega wada miya gwausowala.
\s1 Keliso maꞌetamo ꞌiilama tomota ꞌadi loina manuna
\p 
\v 3 \x * \xo 1:3 \xt 1 Te 1:2-3\x*Gosemao, ꞌilobwenema be tuta yauyauna Yaubada ꞌada lokagutokiye ꞌimi emisa be ꞌimi eobooboboma taumimo ꞌemiya ꞌadi sinabwa manuna.
\v 4 \x * \xo 1:4 \xt 1 Te 2:19-20\x*ꞌEnega toekalesiyao sena yaudi matadiya ꞌatuputupumi, ꞌagwae, “Taudi me Tesalonaika eꞌalamaꞌiꞌita ꞌaledi. ꞌAnabwaꞌayoi ꞌadi talauwalao mwau sinabwana siꞌebwaꞌedi, ta tuwa tuga ma idi ꞌalamaꞌiꞌita be ma idi emisa Yaubada ꞌenaya.”
\p 
\v 5 \x * \xo 1:5 \xt Pi 1:29\x*Gete ꞌebeꞌita be ꞌenega Yaubada ꞌina loina palupaluna tada mwalatoni, manuna ꞌimi miyamwau nidi ꞌediyega ꞌigiepaꞌalimi, be ꞌenega ꞌina ꞌebeloina ꞌana lugu ꞌida lobwenemi.
\v 6 \x * \xo 1:6 \xt Lo 12:19\x*Nadigega wate saꞌi taudi ꞌami togieꞌelouyao ꞌadi eꞌisa Yaubada ꞌigibugibubu be ꞌina gamwasowala sida loba.
\p 
\v 7 \x * \xo 1:7 \xt Md 25:31\x*ꞌOmi tomiyamwau yaeonami ꞌaene maꞌetamo ꞌida ꞌInapwana Yesu galewega ꞌida mwaꞌuta maninima, ma ina aniloseyao ta ꞌawe sabelulu wate ꞌida meꞌe, be ꞌomi ta ꞌaboꞌama ꞌida ꞌebe eyawaiꞌata ꞌida ꞌebwaꞌeda,
\v 8 \x * \xo 1:8 \xt Md 25:41; Lo 2:8\x*ta taudi ꞌida ꞌInapwana Yesu Keliso tetelina siguitoyasena, ga Yaubada siemwagemwageyena, ꞌadi eꞌisa mwauna ꞌida ꞌebwaꞌedi.
\v 9 \x * \xo 1:9 \xt Md 25:41, 46; 2 Pi 3:7\x*ꞌEnega sida miya dumaduma, ta sida esilae ataya ꞌasa gabugabu ꞌenaya, be ꞌInapwana maninina be ꞌina waiwai ta ꞌana tupu geyaꞌabo siꞌitaꞌita.
\v 10 \x * \xo 1:10 \xt Kol 3:4\x*Manuna ꞌabo tuta nina ꞌimamai, ꞌana tupu sinabwana ꞌida loba ꞌina guinuwao ꞌebe nuwaowana manudi ꞌana toemisao ꞌediyega. Ta ꞌomi lowa tetelina ꞌaꞌebwaꞌemi ga waemisena, ꞌenega maꞌetamo ꞌomi maꞌemao Yesu ꞌina apwesama ꞌenaya tada tupu.
\p 
\v 11 \x * \xo 1:11 \xt Kol 1:10\x*Lowa Yaubada ꞌiesinuwemi ga ꞌibwauyemi, ga ꞌenega waemisena. Gete manuna ꞌaboꞌama tuta yauyauna ꞌasidasida manumi be ꞌaene wada muliya ꞌaiꞌaili. Manuna ꞌomi nuwanuwami be emisa ꞌaiꞌailega wada bubuna palupalu, ꞌenega ꞌima sidasida Yaubada ꞌenaya ꞌaene ꞌida giewaiwaiyemi be guinuwa nidi wada guinuwedi.
\v 12 \x * \xo 1:12 \xt 1 Ko 10:31\x*Gete ꞌenega be tomota yaudi ꞌida ꞌInapwana Yesu ꞌana esana situpu, ꞌomi ꞌimi guinuwa boboꞌadi manudi. Ta ꞌomi wate tupu waloba tauna ꞌana esanega, ta tupu nidi maiboꞌana Yaubada be ꞌInapwana Yesu Keliso ꞌidi oboboma ꞌenega.
\c 2
\s1 ꞌEbweu tai toꞌumalina manuna
\p 
\v 1 \x * \xo 2:1 \xt 1 Te 4:13-17\x*Gosemao, nuwanuwama be wada mwalamwalatoni ꞌida ꞌInapwana Yesu Keliso ꞌina apwesa limana be ꞌida egogona ꞌenaya manuna,
\v 2 be ꞌenega geyaꞌabo waꞌateꞌate saꞌala. ꞌEnega ꞌeguma tomota sigwae, “ꞌInapwana ꞌina apwesa limanama ꞌana tuta gete,” geyaꞌabo waemiemisedi. ꞌEguma siona ꞌaene mwalatoi gete silobena ꞌidi madawalega, nai Yaubada ꞌina ona ꞌediya ꞌenega, nai ꞌaboꞌagu ꞌidi leta yaꞌetoladina ꞌediya ꞌenega,
\v 3 \x * \xo 2:3 \xt 2 Te 2:8\x*geyaꞌabo ꞌebweu wate ꞌidi kabo nidi waemiemisedi, ta esi wada nuwaꞌiꞌisi ꞌaene nugana tomota yaudi Yaubada sida etalauwale, be tai toꞌumalina ꞌida apwesa, ta muliyega Yesu ꞌiilama. Onaꞌaiꞌaila, tai nina toꞌumalina ta guguyoi taina,
\v 4 \x * \xo 2:4 \xt Md 24:5; Dan 11:36\x*Yaubada ꞌana saiya ta wate ꞌebe emisa maiboꞌadi ꞌadi saiya, ꞌenega tauna ꞌida gituꞌeye be Yaubada ꞌina Anuwa Tabu ꞌenaya ꞌida miyatowa, be ꞌida etoloina ꞌatuwa Yaubada.
\p 
\v 5 Nai wanuwaꞌiꞌisina ꞌaene lowa ꞌomi maꞌegwao tamiyami ga yage nidi manudi yaeonemi.
\v 6 Ta ꞌomi tai nina toꞌumalina ꞌina mai soꞌisoꞌi ꞌalena, niꞌatu wamwalamwalatoni ꞌaene ꞌeguma ꞌina mai ꞌana tuta ꞌilobai ꞌenega ꞌiapwesama.
\p 
\v 7 Onaꞌaiꞌaila, gete tuga tai toꞌumalina nina ꞌina guinuwao niꞌatu siapweapwesa kwaiya baleꞌuya, ta mali tai saꞌi guinuwa toꞌumalidi nidi ꞌiꞌetoꞌetobodedi be ꞌana laba toꞌetoboda nina ꞌitoolosiꞌi,
\v 8 be ꞌenega totoꞌumalina nina ꞌiapwesama. Muliyega ꞌida ꞌInapwana Yesu ꞌida apwesama, be tai toꞌumalina nina ꞌida loesawali yage ꞌeluwa ꞌediyega, nate ꞌina waiwai ta ꞌawanega ꞌawesabelulu.
\p 
\v 9 \x * \xo 2:9 \xt Md 24:24; Et 13:13\x*Ta tai nina toꞌumalina ꞌida apwesa, be Seitani ꞌina waiwaiyega edeedede ta yage ꞌebe nuwaowana ꞌediyega tomota ꞌida kaboedi.
\v 10-11 Ta taudi tetela ꞌaiꞌaila ꞌana tologuitoyasao ꞌidi sena ꞌasa gabugabu, Yaubada ꞌida tagwaledi be Seitani ꞌina kaboyao maiboꞌana sida emisedi, ta taudi bwaꞌomatana sida loba, manuna eꞌita ꞌaiꞌaila siguitoyasena,
\v 12 ta bubuna geyogeyoi ꞌana guinuwa nuwadi ꞌiꞌewena. ꞌEguma lowa tetela ꞌaiꞌaila sida emisenaya, Yaubada ꞌida ꞌetoseyedi, ta saꞌi nigeya.
\s1 Yaubada ꞌana toesinuwao
\p 
\v 13 \x * \xo 2:13 \xt 1 Te 1:4; Ep 1:4-5; 1 Pi 1:2\x*Gosemao, onaꞌaiꞌaila ꞌida ꞌInapwana ꞌiobobomemi, manuna gimituta ꞌenaya ꞌiesinuwemi be ꞌaene Yaluyaluwa Tabuna ꞌenega ꞌida gieꞌesasemi, be tetela ꞌaiꞌaila wada emise ꞌami ꞌetoseyana manuna, ꞌenega ꞌilobwenema be tuta maiboꞌana manumi ꞌada lokagutoki Yaubada ꞌena.
\v 14 Tetela nina lowa ꞌaloguguyaena ꞌemiya ga waemisena, ga gete ꞌenega ꞌida ꞌInapwana Yesu Keliso ꞌina esaesa ꞌiꞌebwaꞌemi.
\v 15 \x * \xo 2:15 \xt 1 Ko 16:13; Lo 8:30\x*Gosemao, wada toolopaꞌala, be ꞌami eꞌitao nidi ꞌima onega, ta wate ꞌima leta ꞌediyega, wada giyaiꞌiꞌisidi.
\p 
\v 16 \x * \xo 2:16 \xt Ib 13:21; 2 Ko 1:3\x*Tamada Yaubada ꞌioboboma ꞌaiꞌailida, ꞌenega tuta yauna ꞌigiegwausowalida, manuna tanuwayaina yage nidi maꞌetamo manuda ꞌida guinuwedi.
\v 17 Tauna Yaubada be ꞌida ꞌInapwana Yesu Keliso sida giegwausowalimi, ta sida giewaiwaiyemi, be wada gwaunuwa ꞌimi paisewa ꞌediya, ta tuta maiboꞌana ꞌimi onao sida boboꞌana.
\c 3
\s1 Manuma wada sidasida Yaubada ꞌena
\p 
\v 1 \x * \xo 3:1 \xt Lo 15:30-31; Ep 6:19\x*Gosemao, ꞌebweu yage wate nuwanuwama be manuma wasidasida Yaubada ꞌena, be ꞌenega ꞌInapwana tetelina ꞌima loguguyega ꞌida lelewana be ꞌiewaiwai tomota ꞌediya, nadigega lowa ꞌemiya.
\v 2 Ta wada sida wate be totoꞌumalidi ꞌediyega Yaubada ꞌida ꞌetoseyema, manuna ꞌInapwana ꞌana toeyaseyaseyao yaudi.
\v 3 \x * \xo 3:3 \xt Yo 17:15\x*Ta esi ꞌInapwana nina ma ꞌana emisa sawesawenaya be ꞌigiepaꞌalimi, ta ꞌiꞌitaꞌiꞌisimi be ꞌaene geyaꞌabo Seitani ꞌigitogitoomi.
\v 4 ꞌEnega ꞌInapwana ꞌaemisena ꞌaene ꞌima eꞌita ꞌemiya waematamatanedi,
\v 5 \x * \xo 3:5 \xt Ib 12:2\x*ta wate ꞌida gienuwa sabwalenimi, tauna ꞌina oboboma manuna, ta wate ꞌimi toolopaꞌala Keliso ꞌena manuna.
\s1 Logwautoyasa geyaꞌabo
\p 
\v 6 \x * \xo 3:6 \xt 1 Te 5:14\x*Gosemao, ꞌaemataluwemi wate, ꞌida ꞌInapwana Yesu Keliso ꞌana esanega, be ꞌeguma ꞌaina tasidao loogwautoyasidi, geyaꞌabo waꞌitaꞌita naodi, manuna gwautoyasa ꞌina ꞌeda ꞌaboꞌama nigeya ꞌaeꞌieꞌitami, ta gwaunuwa ꞌina ꞌeda esi.
\v 7 \x * \xo 3:7 \xt 1 Te 2:9\x*ꞌEnega niꞌatu wamwalatonina ꞌaene ꞌilobwenemi be ꞌaboꞌama waetotowanema. Manuna lowa ꞌomi maꞌemao tamiyamiya, nigeya ꞌebweu tuta paisewa ꞌena ꞌada logwautoyasa.
\v 8 Nadigega wate taumamo ꞌaeꞌenima. Boiboi be ꞌasiyata ꞌediya ꞌapaipaisewa, manuna geya nuwama be ꞌami mwau ꞌasaꞌu ꞌama masula manuna.
\p 
\v 9 Onaꞌaiꞌaila, loina ꞌimiyami be ꞌomi wada eꞌenima, ta tuwa tuga tauma ꞌama masula manuna ꞌaetaetapewa, be ꞌenega ꞌomi ꞌima guinuwa wada etotowanedi.
\v 10 Ta wate lowa ꞌomi maꞌemao tamiyami, ꞌaloinemi ꞌaene ꞌabo yaita ꞌilogwautoyasa geyaꞌabo wate ꞌiꞌeꞌa.
\p 
\v 11 Niꞌatu tetelimi ꞌanonona ꞌaene ꞌaidi ꞌemiyega tologwautoyasa, ta nigeya sida miyabaula be sida paisewa.
\v 12 \x * \xo 3:12 \xt 1 Te 4:11\x*ꞌEnega gosedao nidi ꞌada emataluwedi, ta ꞌida ꞌInapwana Yesu Keliso ꞌana esanega ꞌaloinedi, be ꞌidi paisewa taudimo sida guinuwedi, ta sida miyabaula be ꞌenega ꞌadi masula sida loba.
\p 
\v 13 \x * \xo 3:13 \xt Ga 6:9; 1 Ko 15:58\x*Gosemao, guinuwa boboꞌadi manudi geyaꞌabo waloꞌameꞌame.
\p 
\v 14 ꞌEguma yaita eꞌita nidi ꞌimi leta gete solanaya ꞌisinalidi, geyaꞌabo tai nina waꞌitaꞌita nao, be ꞌenega ꞌina guinuwa nina manuna ꞌida omayamaya,
\v 15 ta watoo be geyaꞌabo waeetalauwale, manuna tauna tasidai, ꞌenega eꞌita namo waꞌebwaꞌe.
\s1 Ona ꞌana ꞌebe losalowa
\p 
\v 16 \x * \xo 3:16 \xt Yo 14:27\x*ꞌIda ꞌinapwana tauna nuwasiwalowa ꞌalena be ꞌida gienuwa siwalowemi, be ꞌida giegwausowalimi tuta maiboꞌana, ta maꞌemi wada miyaataya.
\p 
\v 17 \x * \xo 3:17 \xt 1 Ko 16:21\x*Leta gete ꞌana ꞌebe losalowa taugu nimaguyega yaꞌetoꞌetoladinawa, nadigega ꞌigu gimi letao ꞌediya.
\v 18 Ta ꞌida ꞌInapwana Yesu Keliso ꞌina oboboma maiboꞌami ꞌemiya.
\cls ꞌAboꞌagu Paulo. 
